Design own buildings on Processing or import buildings designed with other software?
- Importing from other software encourages diversity of tools to attain a goal

Sky made in Processing or composed of multiple images and videos?
- Using images and videos may create more realistic effect
- Designing the sky from scratch allows experimentation and limit testing in reimagining our perceptions

What acoustic atmosphere is desired for the city ground and the sky meditative view?
- Airy and lots of reverb
- Intense and uncomfortable
- Sneaky and thriller
- Mysterious and remote
- Orchestral and vivid

Ways of making the shield of light appear in sky?
- Design simple sky for city light and play with opacity
- Make shield appear on top of star-filled sky

How to make sky in 3D space?
- Do skybox
- Design sky and use translate and rotate

How to make light glow and possibly reflect on things?
- Blur filter (right now blurs the whole canvas though)

